        <content>
          <p>SECTION 2.  OF THE FORM OF DONATIONS INTER VIVOS
Art. 1541.  Form required for donations
A donation inter vivos shall be made by authentic act under the penalty of absolute nullity, unless otherwise expressly permitted by law.</p>
